Package: ARUtools
Type: Package
Title: Tools for management of Autonomous Recording Unit (ARU) data
Version: 0.6.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("David", "Hope", email = "david.hope@ec.gc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
            comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2140-4261")),
    person("Steffi", "LaZerte", email = "sel@steffilazerte.ca", role = c("aut"), 
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7690-8360")))
Description: ARutools is a collection of functions and R code for parsing Autonomous Recording
    Unit (ARU) data and for sub-sampling recordings. Extract Metadata from your recordings,  select a subset of recordings for interpretation, and prepare files for processing on the 'WildTrax' platform.
